==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔːkə(r)|-ɔːkə(r)]]

===Noun===
'''walker'''  (''plural'' walkers)
#a person who [[walk]]s, either as a [[pedestrian]] or in a [[walking]] [[race]]
#a [[framework]] [[device]] used to [[support]] either an [[infant]] [[learning]] to walk, or a person with walking [[difficulties]]
#(''often in plural'') a [[shoe]] designed for [[comfortable]] walking
#a person who walks (or [[waulk]]s) [[cloth]]
